gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 120, Raptors 118
gameRecap.excerpt: Boston defeats Toronto, 120-118, as they win their fifth in a row. Jaylen Brown led Boston with 31 points, a season-high 10 rebounds, and six assists as Derrick White (21 points, five rebounds, seven assists, three steals, two blocks) and Luke Kornet (season-high 20 points) totaled 41. Scottie Barnes led Toronto with 30 points (career-high seven 3PT), 10 rebounds, and five assists while Pascal Siakam added 27 points, five rebounds, and five assists.
